s `Makie`, but that extension depends also on `GraphMakie`, it would be very useful not to make `GraphMakie` a dependency since it's heavy to precompile, but install that alongside `Makie` when the user does `using MyPackage, Makie`. Maybe adding a `Project.toml` for extensions could be good? Not sure if this is already possible somehow but haven't found anything on the topic.

